(
<bibRefCitation author="Owen" box="[301,436,1946,1970]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" refString="Owen, B. (2013) Notes on the correct taxonomic status of Haliotis rugosa Lamarck, 1822, and Haliotis pustulata Reeve, 1846, with description of a new subspecies from Rodrigues Island, Mascarene Islands, Indian Ocean (Mollusca: Vetigastropoda: Haliotidae). Zootaxa, 3646 (2), 189 - 193. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 3646.2.7" type="journal article" year="2013">
