<paragraph blockId="14.[151,1436,1909,2006]" lastBlockId="15.[151,1436,151,213]" lastPageId="15" lastPageNumber="16" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,273,1981,2006]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">Notes.</emphasis>
Although long considered a distinct species, the latest opinion (
<bibRefCitation author="Owen" box="[992,1126,1982,2006]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" refString="Owen, B. (2013) Notes on the correct taxonomic status of Haliotis rugosa Lamarck, 1822, and Haliotis pustulata Reeve, 1846, with description of a new subspecies from Rodrigues Island, Mascarene Islands, Indian Ocean (Mollusca: Vetigastropoda: Haliotidae). Zootaxa, 3646 (2), 189 - 193. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 3646.2.7" type="journal article" year="2013">
Owen 
<number box="[1068,1126,1982,2006]" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" value="2013.0">2013</number>
</bibRefCitation>
) is that 
<taxonomicName box="[1216,1320,1981,2006]" class="Gastropoda" family="Haliotidae" genus="Haliotis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepetellida" pageId="14" pageNumber="15" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="pustulata">
<emphasis box="[1216,1320,1981,2006]" italics="true" pageId="14" pageNumber="15">pustulata</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
should be considered the continental subspecies of the Mascarene 
<taxonomicName box="[793,908,153,176]" class="Gastropoda" family="Haliotidae" genus="Haliotis" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepetellida" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" phylum="Mollusca" rank="species" species="rugosa">
<emphasis box="[793,908,153,176]" italics="true" pageId="15" pageNumber="16">H. rugosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. The similarity and possible synonymy of the two taxa was earlier noted by 
<bibRefCitation author="Herbert" box="[487,669,188,213]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" refString="Herbert, D. G. (1990 a) Designation of lectotype and type locality for Haliotis rugosa Lamarck, 1822 (Mollusca: Gastropoda: Haliotidae). Annals of the Natal Museum, 31, 207 - 213." type="journal article" year="1990" yearSuffix="a">
Herbert (
<number box="[588,649,188,212]" pageId="15" pageNumber="16" value="1990.0">1990</number>
a)
</bibRefCitation>
.
</paragraph>
